discussion app:

responsibilities:
|
|----------------create or start a discussion -------------------------(1)
|----------------view a discussion ------------------------------------(2)
|----------------delete a discussion ----------------------------------(3)
|----------------update a discussion ----------------------------------(4)
|----------------reply to a discussion --------------------------------(5)
|----------------convert public discussion to private -----------------(6)
|----------------convert private discussion to public -----------------(7)

actions:

(2)
 |
 |---------------share discussion -------------------------------------(#000000)
                 |
                 |----------facebook
                 |----------twitter
                 |----------G plus
                 |----------other analysers
 |
 |---------------add to  watchlist ------------------------------------(#000001)
 |
 |---------------report discussion ------------------------------------(#000002)
 |
 |---------------upvote -----------------------------------------------(#000003)
 |
 |---------------follow post ------------------------------------------(#000004)
 |
 |---------------ask analysers to join --------------------------------(#000005)

